<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Trumpeter" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Trumpeter,</orth> one who sounds a trumpet: <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.2.1" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 2, 1</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.121" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 121</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 4.8.35" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 8, 35</bibl>. Metaphorically, one who proclaims and publishes: <cit><quote>to be --s of our unlawful intents,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.32" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 3, 32</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>